# Changelog

All notable changes to `<PROJECT_NAME>` are documented here.
Format follows [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/).

See also: [`README.md`](README.md) for project orientation;
[`ARCHITECTURE.md`](ARCHITECTURE.md) for the design that much of the
work below evolves; [`docs/CAPABILITIES.md`](docs/CAPABILITIES.md) for
the operator-facing capabilities + known limitations.

