### Fixed (`<EXAMPLE: capability matrix declared X unsupported but the codec actually rendered it>`)

`<RATIONALE — describe the failure mode the user / operator was
seeing and why the fix matters.  Honest framing: don't oversell the
fix; acknowledge if the bug had been latent for N weeks.>`

* **Commit `<SHA>`** — `<the root cause + the fix>`.  `<reference to
  the test that pins the corrected behaviour>`.
* **Commit `<SHA>`** — `<companion doc-sync update if applicable —
  CAPABILITIES.md, ARCHITECTURE.md, etc.>`.

`<TEST IMPACT — how many regression-guard tests were added>`.

